snippet.title: Tennis on Court - Official Trailer | Perp Games VR Summer Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Here's a look at character customization options, game modes, gameplay, and more in this latest trailer for Tennis on Court. Tennis on Court will be available on PlayStation VR2 in summer 2023.
